Class MaxPanelistConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • symposium.model.Constraint
      • symposium.model.MaxPanelistConstraint

  • public class MaxPanelistConstraint
extends Constraint
    The class MaxPanelistConstraint inherits from Constraint. Max number of Panelists is violated when a panelist appears more than the set maximum number of times per day.
